{{!
Derived from A+ (a-plus/edit_course/templates/edit_course/edit_content.html).

Context variables:
* autosetupurl (string) URL to the automatic setup page
* categories (array of stdClass objects), each object has fields
    - name (string)
    - editurl (string) URL to category edit page
    - removeurl (string) URL for deleting the category
    - statusready (bool) true if ready
    - statusstr (string) human-readable status
* createcategoryurl (string) URL for creating a new category
* coursemodules (array of objects), each object has fields
    - name (string) with ordinal number
    - statusready (bool) true if ready
    - statusstr (string) status as human-readable string
    - editurl (string) URL for editing the round
    - removeurl (string) URL for deleting the round
    - url (string) URL for viewing the round
    - addnewexerciseurl (string) URL for adding a new exercise to the round
    - addnewchapterurl (string) URL for adding a new chapter to the round
    - allexercises (array of objects) all learning objects (exercises/chapters) of the round,
            includes also hidden objects, each object has fields
        * name (string) with ordinal number
        * statusready (bool) true if status is ready
        * statusstr (string) status as human-readable string
        * editurl (string) URL for editing the exercise
        * removeurl (string) URL for deleting the exercise
        * displayurl (string) URL for viewing the exercise (if the exercise is embedded
          to a chapter, then the link opens the chapter)
        * submissionlisturl (string) URL to the all submissions list
* createmoduleurl (string) URL for creating a new exercise round
* renumberactionurl (string) URL for form action that renumbers exercises
* modulenumberingoptions (callable), returns the HTML <option> elements for module numbering
        (in <select> element of the form).
* contentnumberingoptions (callable), returns the HTML <option> elements for content numbering
        (in <select> element of the form).
}}

<div class="card bg-light">
  <div class="card-body">
  <form method="post" class="form-inline" action="{{{ renumberactionurl }}}">
    <a href="{{{ autosetupurl }}}" class="btn btn-secondary mr-2">{{#str}} autosetup, mod_adastra {{/str}}</a>
    <!--
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="submit" name="cache">{{#str}} clearcontentcache, mod_adastra {{/str}}</button>
    -->
  </form>
  </div>
</div>

